                  </hi>. I am a corn-dealer. I bought the chaise from Mr. Cochrane for 9<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350615-name-245" type="witnessName">
