               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner to</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">THOMAS WILLIAM LLOYD, JUN</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> When I selected out this chaise, what reply did you make on the price of the chaise? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> The price was not asked—I will swear I did not say 12<hi rend="italic">l</hi>,—it appeared very much broken.</p>
